:name:
Incubation

:coretxt:
You have taken on to yourself to learn new secret.
It might be something that you could not learn normal means.
Maybe there is no willing teacher or nobody even knows such secret.
Relevant ability is chosen.
When you have enogh time, you can use that time to learn the secret.
Three succesful rolls are required.
After those this secret is replaces with the target one.
Some other penalties may apply when learning.
This is way to circumvent some requirements.

:requirements:
Cannot learn some ability due some restrictions.

:tags:
Universal
